Fvwm is a powerful window manager.  Version 2.5.21 is a beta
release that fixes a bug in 2.5.20.  Please be aware that any
features introduced in the 2.5.x development versions may be
renamed, changed or removed without notice before 2.6.0.

Upgrading from 2.5.20 is strongly recommended; upgrading from
earlier 2.5.x versions is recommended.

This release is available at the home page: http://www.fvwm.org/.

* New features:

   - The command Scroll can now be used for interactive scrolling.

* Bug Fixes:

   - Fixed Tile...Placement styles (SmartPlacement) that were
     broken in 2.5.20.
